{"url":"https://jsg-system.com/company/","html":"<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"ja\" prefix=\"og: http://ogp.me/ns#\">\n<head>\n<!-- Google tag (gtag.js) -->\n<script async src=\"https://www.googletagmanager.com/gtag/js?id=G-JKY286QSC5\"></script>\n<script>\n  window.dataLayer = window.dataLayer || [];\n  function gtag(){dataLayer.push(arguments);}\n  gtag('js', new Date());\n\n  gtag('config', 'G-JKY286QSC5');\n</script>\n\n<meta charset=\"utf-8\" />\n<meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width\">\n<meta name=\"format-detection\" content=\"telephone=no\">\n\n<link rel=\"icon\" href=\"https://jsg-system.com/wordpress/wp-content/themes/nkh/common/images/favicon.ico\" />\n<link rel=\"apple-touch-icon\" href=\"webclip.png\" />\n\n<title>企業情報｜日本海警備保障株式会社</title>\n<meta name=\"description\" content=\"創業50年以上の実績のある日本海警備保障の企業情報ページです。会社に関係するすべての皆様を大切にし、地域に根差し、人を介して「安心・安全」を提供する警備会社としてさらなる発展を目指し歩みを進めて参ります。\" />\n\n<!-- OGP -->\n<meta property=\"og:url\" content=\"https://jsg-system.com/company/\" />\n<meta property=\"og:type\" content=\"article\" />\n<meta property=\"og:title\" content=\"企業情報｜日本海警備保障株式会社\" />\n<meta property=\"og:description\" content=\"創業50年以上の実績のある日本海警備保障の企業情報ページです。会社に関係するすべての皆様を大切にし、地域に根差し、人を介して「安心・安全」を提供する警備会社としてさらなる発展を目指し歩みを進めて参ります。\" />\n<meta property=\"og:site_name\" content=\"日本海警備保障株式会社\" />\n<meta property=\"og:image\" content=\"https://jsg-system.com/wordpress/wp-content/themes/nkh/common/images/ogp.png\" />\n\n<link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"https://jsg-system.com/wordpress/wp-content/themes/nkh/common/css/reset.css\">\n<link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"https://jsg-system.com/wordpress/wp-content/themes/nkh/common/css/design.css\">\n<link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"https://jsg-system.com/wordpress/wp-content/themes/nkh/common/css/sub.css\">\n    \n<script src=\"https://ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/jquery/3.1.1/jquery.min.js\"></script>\n<script type=\"text/javascript\" src=\"https://jsg-system.com/wordpress/wp-content/themes/nkh/common/js/common.js\" defer></script>\n\n<link rel=\"preconnect\" href=\"https://fonts.googleapis.com\">\n<link rel=\"preconnect\" href=\"https://fonts.gstatic.com\" crossorigin>\n<link href=\"https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Noto+Sans+JP:wght@400;500;700&family=Noto+Serif+JP:wght@400;500;600;700;900&display=swap\" rel=\"stylesheet\">\n    \n<link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/animate.css/3.6.2/animate.min.css\" />\n<script src=\"https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/wow/1.1.2/wow.min.js\"></script>\n    \n<!--[if lt IE 9]>\n<script src=\"common/js/html5shiv.js\"></script>\n<![endif]-->\n\n</head>\n<body class=\"subpage company page_company\">\n\n<header class=\"header\">\n    <h1 class=\"logo\"><a href=\"/\"><img src=\"/wordpress/wp-content/themes/nkh/common/images/logo.svg\" alt=\"日本海警備保障\"></a></h1>\n    <div class=\"header_rightbox\">\n        <nav class=\"header_nav\">\n            <ul>\n                <li class=\"page_index\"><a href=\"/\">HOME</a></li>\n                <li class=\"page_company\"><a href=\"/company/\">企業情報</a></li>\n                <li class=\"header_nav_parent page_service\"><a href=\"javascript: void(0)\">サービス紹介<span></span></a>\n                    <ul class=\"header_nav_child\">\n                        <li><a href=\"/institution/\">施設警備</a></li>\n                        <li><a href=\"/machine/\">機械警備</a></li>\n                        <li><a href=\"/traffic_guidance/\">交通誘導警備</a></li>\n                    </ul>\n                </li>\n                <li class=\"page_info\"><a href=\"/info/\">お知らせ</a></li>\n            </ul>\n        </nav>\n        <a class=\"btn_rock\" href=\"https://jsg-system.com/works/\"><span></span>社員用</a>\n        <a class=\"btn_contact\" href=\"/contact/\"><span></span>お問い合わせ</a>\n        <div class=\"sp_x\"><div class=\"x_box\"><span></span><span></span><span></span></div></div>\n    </div>\n</header>\n<div class=\"sp_nav\">\n    <nav>\n        <ul>\n            <li><a href=\"/\">HOME</a></li>\n            <li><a href=\"/company/\">企業情報</a></li>\n            <li><a href=\"javascript: void(0)\" class=\"sp_nav_parent\">サービス紹介</a>\n                <div class=\"sp_nav_child\"><a href=\"/institution/\">施設警備</a></div>\n                <div class=\"sp_nav_child\"><a href=\"/machine/\">機械警備</a></div>\n                <div class=\"sp_nav_child mgb10\"><a href=\"/traffic_guidance/\">交通誘導警備</a></div>\n            </li>\n            <li><a href=\"/info/\">お知らせ</a></li>\n        </ul>\n        <div class=\"sp_otherbtn\">\n            <a href=\"/contact/\" class=\"sp_nav_contact\"><span>お問い合わせ</span></a>\n            <a href=\"https://jsg-system.com/works/\" class=\"sp_nav_rock\"><span>社員用</span></a>\n        </div>\n    </nav>\n</div>\n    \n<div class=\"sub_header gradation\">\n    <div class=\"inner\">\n        <h1>COMPANY<span>企業情報</span></h1>\n    </div>\n    <img src=\"/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/subh_company.png\" alt=\"\">\n</div>\n<div class=\"subpage_wrap\">\n    <section>\n\n    \n<div class=\"wp-block-group sub_inner\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container is-layout-constrained wp-block-group-is-layout-constrained\">\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading min\">代表挨拶</h2>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group company_lead\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container is-layout-constrained wp-block-group-is-layout-constrained\">\n<p><span>人を大切に、人を介して、地域に根差して</span></p>\n\n\n\n<p>目まぐるしく変化する現代社会。テクノロジーの進歩によるこれまで想定されていなかった事件の発生、世界的な気候変動による大規模災害、日本における急速な人口減少、そして2020年から世界中を覆いつくした新型コロナウイルス感染症。<br>そんな予測困難な現代において、当社は創立以来、地域に根差し、人を介して多くの方々に「安心・安全」を提供して参りました。<br>おかげさまで、当社は2023年で創立50周年を迎えます。<br>これからも、会社に関係するすべての皆様を大切にし、地域に根差し、人を介して「安心・安全」を提供する警備会社としてさらなる発展を目指し歩みを進めて参ります。</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group align_right\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container is-layout-constrained wp-block-group-is-layout-constrained\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full signiture\"><img fetchpriority=\"high\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"622\" height=\"207\" src=\"https://jsg-system.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/signiture.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-197\" srcset=\"https://jsg-system.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/signiture.png 622w, https://jsg-system.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/signiture-300x100.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 622px) 100vw, 622px\" /></figure>\n</div></div>\n</div></div>\n</div></div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group sub_inner\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container is-layout-constrained wp-block-group-is-layout-constrained\">\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading min\">会社概要</h2>\n\n\n\n<dl class=\"wp-block-simple-definition-list-blocks-list company_table\">\n<dt class=\"wp-block-simple-definition-list-blocks-term\">商号</dt>\n\n\n\n<dd class=\"wp-block-simple-definition-list-blocks-details\">日本海警備保障株式会社</dd>\n\n\n\n<dt class=\"wp-block-simple-definition-list-blocks-term\">所在地</dt>\n\n\n\n<dd class=\"wp-block-simple-definition-list-blocks-details\">〒920-0376　石川県金沢市福増町北1377番地2</dd>\n\n\n\n<dt class=\"wp-block-simple-definition-list-blocks-term\">設立</dt>\n\n\n\n<dd class=\"wp-block-simple-definition-list-blocks-details\">1973年11月1日</dd>\n\n\n\n<dt class=\"wp-block-simple-definition-list-blocks-term\">代表者</dt>\n\n\n\n<dd class=\"wp-block-simple-definition-list-blocks-details\">稲原　淳</dd>\n\n\n\n<dt class=\"wp-block-simple-definition-list-blocks-term\">事業内容</dt>\n\n\n\n<dd class=\"wp-block-simple-definition-list-blocks-details\">施設警備業務　機械警備業務　交通誘導警備業務</dd>\n\n\n\n<dt class=\"wp-block-simple-definition-list-blocks-term\">資本金</dt>\n\n\n\n<dd class=\"wp-block-simple-definition-list-blocks-details\">3,000万円</dd>\n\n\n\n<dt class=\"wp-block-simple-definition-list-blocks-term\">従業員数</dt>\n\n\n\n<dd class=\"wp-block-simple-definition-list-blocks-details\">140名（2023年10月末現在）</dd>\n\n\n\n<dt class=\"wp-block-simple-definition-list-blocks-term\">認定</dt>\n\n\n\n<dd class=\"wp-block-simple-definition-list-blocks-details\">認定 石川県公安委員会 第５１００００２７号</dd>\n\n\n\n<dt class=\"wp-block-simple-definition-list-blocks-term\">加盟団体</dt>\n\n\n\n<dd class=\"wp-block-simple-definition-list-blocks-details\">一般社団法人石川県警備業協会</dd>\n\n\n\n<dt class=\"wp-block-simple-definition-list-blocks-term\">取引銀行</dt>\n\n\n\n<dd class=\"wp-block-simple-definition-list-blocks-details\">北國銀行　金沢信用金庫</dd>\n</dl>\n</div></div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group sub_inner\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container is-layout-constrained wp-block-group-is-layout-constrained\">\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading min\">沿革</h2>\n\n\n\n<dl class=\"wp-block-simple-definition-list-blocks-list company_history\">\n<dt class=\"wp-block-simple-definition-list-blocks-term\">昭和48年11月</dt>\n\n\n\n<dd class=\"wp-block-simple-definition-list-blocks-details\">金沢市小坂町にて設立　資本金3,000千円<br>羽咋市に能登警備本部を設置</dd>\n\n\n\n<dt class=\"wp-block-simple-definition-list-blocks-term\">昭和58年4月</dt>\n\n\n\n<dd class=\"wp-block-simple-definition-list-blocks-details\">石川県公安委員会より警備業法の認定</dd>\n\n\n\n<dt class=\"wp-block-simple-definition-list-blocks-term\">昭和58年11月</dt>\n\n\n\n<dd class=\"wp-block-simple-definition-list-blocks-details\">資本金17,200千円に増資</dd>\n\n\n\n<dt class=\"wp-block-simple-definition-list-blocks-term\">昭和59年7月</dt>\n\n\n\n<dd class=\"wp-block-simple-definition-list-blocks-details\">金沢市北安江に移転</dd>\n\n\n\n<dt class=\"wp-block-simple-definition-list-blocks-term\">昭和59年11月</dt>\n\n\n\n<dd class=\"wp-block-simple-definition-list-blocks-details\">資本金21,000千円に増資</dd>\n\n\n\n<dt class=\"wp-block-simple-definition-list-blocks-term\">平成11年5月</dt>\n\n\n\n<dd class=\"wp-block-simple-definition-list-blocks-details\">資本金30,000千円に増資</dd>\n\n\n\n<dt class=\"wp-block-simple-definition-list-blocks-term\">平成23年4月</dt>\n\n\n\n<dd class=\"wp-block-simple-definition-list-blocks-details\">金沢市福増町北(現在地)に移転</dd>\n</dl>\n</div></div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group sub_inner\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container is-layout-constrained wp-block-group-is-layout-constrained\">\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading min\">標識</h2>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large hyoshiki\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"556\" src=\"https://jsg-system.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/image-1024x556.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-343\" srcset=\"https://jsg-system.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/image-1024x556.png 1024w, https://jsg-system.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/image-300x163.png 300w, https://jsg-system.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/image-768x417.png 768w, https://jsg-system.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/image.png 1414w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" /></figure>\n</div></div>\n        \n    </section>\n</div>\n<div class=\"bread\">\n    <div class=\"inner\">\n        <ul>\n            <li><a href=\"/\">HOME</a></li>\n            <li>企業情報</li>\n        </ul>\n    </div>\n</div>\n        \n\n<footer>\n    <div class=\"footer_contact\">\n        <div class=\"inner\">\n            <a href=\"/contact/\"><span>お問い合わせ</span></a>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"footer_info\">\n        <div class=\"inner\">\n            <div class=\"footer_info_box\">\n                <div class=\"footer_signiture\">\n                    <div class=\"footer_tit\"><img src=\"/wordpress/wp-content/themes/nkh/common/images/logo.svg\" alt=\"日本海警備保障\"></div>\n                    <div class=\"footer_address\">\n                        〒920-0376<br>\n                        石川県金沢市福増町北1377番地2<br>\n                        電話番号：076-255-7711<br>\n                        FAX番号：076-255-7195\n                    </div>\n\t\t\t\t<!--\n                    <div class=\"footer_sns\">\n                        <a href=\"\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://jsg-system.com/wordpress/wp-content/themes/nkh/common/images/sns_tw.svg\" alt=\"\"></a>\n                        <a href=\"\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://jsg-system.com/wordpress/wp-content/themes/nkh/common/images/sns_fb.svg\" alt=\"\"></a>\n                    </div>\n-->\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"footer_link\">\n                    <div class=\"footer_nav\">\n                        <nav>\n                            <ul>\n                                <li><a href=\"/\">HOME</a></li>\n                            </ul>\n                            <ul>\n                                <li><a href=\"/company/\">企業情報</a></li>\n                            </ul>\n                            <ul>\n                                <li><a href=\"javascript: void(0)\" class=\"nolink\">サービス紹介</a></li>\n                                <li class=\"footernav_child\"><a href=\"/institution/\">施設警備</a></li>\n                                <li class=\"footernav_child\"><a href=\"/machine/\">機械警備</a></li>\n                                <li class=\"footernav_child\"><a href=\"/traffic_guidance/\">交通誘導警備</a></li>\n                            </ul>\n                            <ul>\n                                <li><a href=\"/info/\">お知らせ</a></li>\n                            </ul>\n                        </nav>\n                    </div>\n                    <div class=\"footer_key\">\n                        <a href=\"https://jsg-system.com/works/\"><span>社員用</span></a>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"signiture\">&copy; 日本海警備保障株式会社</div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</footer>\n\n<div class=\"pagetop\"><img src=\"https://jsg-system.com/wordpress/wp-content/themes/nkh/common/images/pagetop.svg\" alt=\"\"></div>\n\n<script>\nnew WOW().init();\n</script>\n\n</body>\n</html>","finalUrl":"https://jsg-system.com/company/","rendered":false,"_cachedAt":"2026-06-17T23:27:08.837Z"}